Since 1980, Superior Cabinets has been designing, building, and installing dream kitchens. Work with one of Superior Cabinetsâ€™ Expert Kitchen Designers, who can help you plan, design, and order your cabinets. Every job is made-to-order, designed and personalized specifically for your lifestyle, space, and budget. 

Superior Cabinets sells through their kitchen design showrooms in Calgary, Edmonton, Saskatoon, and Regina, leveraging their cabinet production facility in Saskatoon, Saskatchewan. Make Superior Cabinets your first stop. Family Owned and Operated Since 1980. Superior Cabinets Calgary is an Authorized Dealer of Stonewood Bathroom Vanities.
